    "119439794": {
      "title": "Supergravity couplings: a geometric formulation",
      "abstract": "Abstract This report provides a pedagogical introduction to the description of the general Poincare supergravity/matter/Yang–Mills couplings using methods of Kahler superspace geometry. At a more advanced level this approach is generalized to include tensor field and Chern–Simons couplings in supersymmetry and supergravity, relevant in the context of weakly and strongly coupled string theories."
